programme.title: The Bells Of Death
programme.desc: This genuine martial arts classic sees young Wu Ma learn the way of the sword before heading out to avenge the murder of his family.

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor. He is besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister. The Prime Minister is corrupt, causing them to revolt the throne.

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: When Jianying discovers the Zhao clan's fortune will be left to his brother Yulong, a wandering swordsman, he engineers his parents' death and sends his own son out to kill Yulong.

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Legend Of The Bat
programme.desc: Charismatic swordsman Chu Liu Hsiang, whose battlefield exploits rival his bedroom antics, travels to the Island of Bats, where he encounters monks, women and plenty of action!

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent.

programme.title: Four Riders
programme.desc: Four martial arts experts live in Seoul after the Korean War in the 1950s. One of them inexplicably crosses path with a drug trafficking syndicate, and his three friends have no choice but to fight on his side.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: An award winning movie for best script and best editing. Another tale of a Sino-Japanese war that artistically and emotional triumphed, it clearly portrays the life of wartime.

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with mysterious strength who robs from the rich and gives to the poor. One night, he is ambushed and poisoned by the evil bounty hunter. Can he escape?

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: Another film inspired by the Chinese classic tale Journey to the West. This memorable version presents a unique interpretation with humour, action, and fantasy galore.

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: This is a story of adolescent playfulness and innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together, but rivalry intervenes when they discover boys!

programme.title: The Secret Of The Dirk
programme.desc: The inhabitants of the City of Liu are forced to flee when the vicious Black Tigers gang raids their city, but are able to hide all their gold and treasures in a valley.

programme.title: Duel Of Fist
programme.desc: At his fathers deathbed, David Chiang discovers that he has a half brother in Thailand. He travels to find his long lost brother (Ti Lung), who becomes a boxer in order to earn money for his sick mother.

programme.title: Family Light Affair
programme.desc: After his hit directorial debut Let's Make Laugh, Alfred Cheung Kin-ting returns with this comedic clash of cultures when a Mainland Chinese peasant takes his family to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Descendant Of The Sun
programme.desc: A magic solar baby (Derek Yee) is sent Earthbound by a benevolent god and raised by an old carpenter. He has martial arts superpowers and ''green kryptonite'' loses them during solar eclipses.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a General's daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates.

programme.title: Disciples Of Shaolin
programme.desc: A penniless bumpkin from the country (Fu Sheng) fights his way to quick riches in the city as an enforcer for a textile factory that's threatened by a competitor.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: An amusing insider's look at the Hong Kong film industry from Li Han Hsiang, recreating some of the era's funniest and most surreal stories ripped straight from the gossip.

programme.title: Return To The 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of 'scaffolding kung fu'.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: The music and magic of The Singing Escort is a great showcase for Betty Ting Pei's on-screen appeal. Ting playing Susan, a young woman hiding from her father.

programme.title: All Men Are Brothers
programme.desc: The patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: The Tiger And The Widow
programme.desc: In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: Killer Clans
programme.desc: Based on a popular swordplay novel, this colorful and complex saga has enough conspiracies, stratagems, and sword fights to fascinate even novice kung-fu cinema viewers.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: David is falling in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming. Out of jealousy, Mona lies to him about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Legendary actress Lin Feng Jiao stars in this romantic comedy as an unlikely romance occurs between an entrepreneur's son and a kindergarten's principal's niece.

programme.title: Diary Of A Lady-Killer
programme.desc: This story is a murder mystery mixed with erotica. Each time a local playboy has an affair, the lady shows up dead, making him the prime suspect.

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: After their parents are murdered, twin brothers are separated and raised in wildly different environments, only to both set off in search of revenge in this kung fu classic.

programme.title: My Name Ain't Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated.

programme.title: Return Of Reincarnated...
programme.desc: A band of ruthless ninjas slaughters the entire Wu Dong clan and frames Du Gu Wu Di, chief of the Invincible Clan, for the deed. Yun Fei Yang masters the silkworm martial arts style and takes revenge on Wu Di.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Set on the eve of the Japanese invasion of HK, this tragic Shaw Brothers romance stars Li Ting and Kwan Shan as young lovers torn apart by war.

programme.title: Have Sword Will Travel
programme.desc: When the head of a manor loses his kung fu skills, he enlists his nephew and his fiance to help escort gold to the capital. The duo run into a mysterious knight along the way and prevent bandits from stealing the gold.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps.

programme.title: The Gambling Syndicate
programme.desc: A young provincial detective seeks to take down a local gambling syndicate with the help of two convicts.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles. Their children fall in love, they have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: The Weird Man
programme.desc: During the Three Kingdoms period, a Taoist priest Yu Ji cures many patients with his supernatural powers. However, the arrogant general Sun Che thinks that Yu Ji bewitches people and orders for him to be beheaded.

programme.title: When The Clouds Roll By

Di setiap episode, mereka membantu teman mereka dengan masalah mereka, dan mendapatkan lencana persahabatan (saat ini, mereka mendapatkan Cube-Cubes) atas kesuksesan mereka. Melalui petualangan mereka inilah, Superbook membawa pesan Alkitab kepada generasi anak-anak di era digital.

Program dikemas secara ringan dan menghibur serta diharapkan dapat membangun rasa empati serta simpati pemirsa terhadap hewan.

Ada juga beberapa karakter baru, seperti kru perbaikan terbaik di pulau, yaitu Carly the Crane dan Sandy the Rail Speeder.

programme.desc: Secret Jouju menceritakan tentang seorang peri bernama Jouju yang dikunci dari Negeri Dongeng dan dikirim ke dunia manusia, dia menangani misi dan penyihir dengan kekuatan sihir dan persahabatan.

programme.title: BARBIE IT TAKES TWO
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang diadaptasi dari film televisi streaming Barbie: Big City, Big Dreams. Program ini bercerita mengenai Brooklyn dan Malibu yang merupakan sepasang sahabat, dimana mereka memulai petualangan terbaru mereka dari pantai ke kota besar, dengan diikuti perjalanan sepasang teman yang keren mereka berdua bersenang – senang, berbagi perhatian serta mengejar mimpi bermusik di New York City.

programme.title: LEGO NINJAGO DRAGON RISING
programme.desc: Beberapa tahun setelah Ninjago, sebuah fenomena yang dikenal sebagai The Merge menempatkan ketujuh belas alam ciptaan di planet Ninjago, menimbulkan ancaman baru dan menyebabkan gempa susulan yang kacau yang disebut Mergequakes. Lloyd berteman dengan dua warga sipil Arin dan Sora, mantan penggemar Ninja dan yang terakhir adalah teknopat dari kerajaan totaliter Imperium. Ketiganya ditugaskan untuk menemukan sisa Ninja yang tersebar dan memerangi Claws of Imperium, yang mendambakan Naga Sumber untuk menguras energi unsur mereka sebagai sumber daya.

programme.title: SMURF
programme.desc: Di tengah hutan belantara, terdapat desa rahasia dihuni oleh sekelompok makhluk kecil berwarna biru yang dipimpin oleh Papa Smurf. Kedatangan penyihir jahat Gargamel dan kucingnya, Azrael, merusak kedamaian desa tersebut. Sehingga para Smurf harus mencari cara agar tidak ditangkap oleh Gargamel dan Azrael

programme.title: TRUNGTUNG
programme.desc: Program animasi Indonesia dengan tokoh utama sebuah mobil pick up berwarna kuning yang membahas tentang adab dalam berkendara, mengajarkan tentang aturan dalam berlalu lintas dan akibat dari tidak mematuhi aturan dalam berkendara.

programme.title: ADIT SOPO JARWO
programme.desc: Animasi Indonesia, berisikan kisah kehidupan sehari-hari masyarakat Indonesia yang dipenuhi dengan pengetahuan, kelucuan, kisah persahabatan, serta nilai persatuan, kesatuan, dan kebudayaan. Tokoh dalam cerita ini diantaranya Adit, Adelya, Dennis, Mitha, Devi, Bang Sopo & Bang Jarwo, serta masih banyak lagi

programme.title: BOBOIBOY
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang mengisahkan Boboiboy dan teman-temannya yakni Gopal, Ying, dan Yaya yang masing-masing memiliki kekuatan super. Dengan kekuatan yang dimiliki mereka mencegah Adu Du mencuri biji kakao Tok Aba yang digunakan sebagai sumber energi. Selain itu, Boboiboy dan teman-temannya menjadi pahlawan super dalam menumpas kejahatan dan menjaga kedamaian Bumi.

programme.title: SMURF
programme.desc: Di tengah hutan belantara, terdapat desa rahasia dihuni oleh sekelompok makhluk kecil berwarna biru yang dipimpin oleh Papa Smurf. Para Smurf tinggal di rumah berbentuk jamur dan hidup dengan damai. Ada beberapa karakter smurf lain nya seperti Wild Smurf yang memiliki sifat yang nakal dan memiliki hubungan yang kuat dengan kehidupan hewan, juga temperamen tetapi dia memiliki cara yang aneh terhadap rutinitas harian Smurf berbeda dengan para Smurf lainnya. Karakter lainnya yaitu Leaf, seorang peri alam yang ditakdirkan untuk menggantikan Mother Nature (pada musim pertama) yang belum memiliki kendali penuh atas kekuatannya.

Mereka dikirim ke dunia manusia dan harus menghabiskan sepuluh masa kehidupan untuk berlatih diri menjadi lebih religius untuk menebus dosa dosanya

Walaupun demikian, tidak membuat Toyib mengurungkan impiannya untuk menjadi seorang Jagoan Silat. Banyak drama, pesan moral serta hikmah yang dapat diambil pada program ini.
